  "methodology": "Assessment integrates macro backdrop (growth/recession themes, tariff escalation) with sector-specific dynamics (housing cycle, interest rate sensitivity, building materials tariff exposure). Company-specific fundamentals noted but considered secondary to macro structural forces given current environment.",
